title: Chapter1_Overworld
---
// TODO: Load these from the script... Will need to figure that out in the next related task
// When the Dialogue Control switches to new scenes, it should "reload" the yarn script we're loading in
<<declare $name = "Merk">>
<<declare $checked_for_permit = false>>
<<declare $talked_to_old_man = false>>
<<declare $talked_to_sad_guard = false>>
===

title: NPC1
---
Jerry: Ey kid... boy, lot of us sure are lookin' worse for wear.
Jerry: Military sure is convinced they need to give everything to the soldiers but they're forgettin' about their people... *grumble grumble*
===

title: NPC2
---
Miranda: Stop talkin' to randos out on the street... everyone's here to fend for 'em selves.
Miranda: *She tosses you an apple*
Miranda: Be on your way, kid.
===

title: NPC3
---
Some Dude: Gah... the lines haven't been this long in years!!
Some Dude: That damned population increase...
===

title: NPC4
position: 59,-261
