NPC5: <Conversation with NPC 5>
===

title: CitadelGuard
---
// I'm structuring booleans such that the first event is what we check first
// TODO: Branching dialogue options, maybe?
<<if $talked_to_old_man == false && $talked_to_sad_guard == false>>
  Citadel Guard: Permit, please...
  Citadel Guard: No permit? No entry!
  <<set $checked_for_permit to true>>
<<elseif $talked_to_sad_guard == true>>
  Citadel Guard: I'm on my break...
<<else>> // if talked_to_old_man is true
  Citadel Guard: I told you, you can't come in without a permit!
  <<trigger_animation "old_man_approaches_at_gate">>
<<endif>>
===

title: OldMan
---
Old Man: Ah, hello there young fellow!
<<set $talked_to_old_man to true>>
===

title: SadGuard
---
// TODO: I think I should set a flag that's more like "cheered_up_sad_guard"
// But right now, you can only talk to one of them anyway so it works
<<if $talked_to_sad_guard == false>>
  Sad Guard: I'm told I can't just let people in even if they need it and it's weighing me down...
  -> You: Hey you're just doing your job, sometimes things have to be the way they are
  -> You: I know the feeling of wanting to help when you just can't...
  You: But surely there are ways you can use the rules to help others who don't know them as well as you?
  Sad Guard: You're right! There are some ways people can get in without their own permit... I'll just have to be careful
  <<set $talked_to_sad_guard to true>>
  <<trigger_animation "sad_guard_replaces_other_guard">>
<<else>>
  Sad Guard: I really want to let you in but I don't want to get in trouble.
  Sad Guard: However, if you can find someone that allows a second person in... *wink*
  <<trigger_animation "old_man_approaches_at_gate">>
<<endif>>

===

title: OldManCitadelEnter
---
<<if $talked_to_old_man == true>>
Old Man: Ah, this here is my hired help!
Old Man: I have a secondary designation on my permit somewhere...
Citadel Guard: Looks good then, carry on. Make sure to stick with your employer next time...
<<elseif $talked_to_sad_guard == true>>
Old Man: I happen to have a secondary designation! Young fellow, would you mind giving me a hand?
Sad Guard: That works for me! Carry on- and thanks for the chat.
<<endif>>
===
